<title>TRUST AND OBEY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Thu vak a chun,
 Amah tawh I len tieng;
 Lopi na'n I lampi a salhvak!
 A deih bang I bawl tieng,
 I kawmah A um zing,
 A thu ging leh zuite cheng kiengah.

[V2]
 Gingin, zuiin lampi dang a um puoi,
 Isu a kipahna di'n, gin leh zuih ngal loh chuh.

[V3]
 2. Thimna a um thei puoi,
 Meipi le zing theilo;
 Nuih melin kintak in A nawh mang,
 Ginlah, lauhna umlo;
 Luonthi nulna um lo,
 A thu I gina, I zuih u chun.

[V4]
 3. I lunggil gikpuok cheng,
 Leh I lungkhamna cheng;
 I sepgimna Ama'n ei din ding,
 Lungkhamna leh mauna;
 Dahna buoina umlo,
 A ging leh zuite di'n vangphatna.

[V5]
 4. A hehpih kipahum,
 Zie I genchien thei puoi;
 Amah dinga I kipumpiek ma'n,
 Ei deihsakna haw leh;
 Kipahna ei piek chuh,

[V6]
 5. Lungguola kivawp in,
 A keng bulah chu'i tiu;
 Amah tawh lampi a chieh in,
 Amah thu'n nung hitiu;
 Ei sawlna a chieh in,
 Laukiu, A thu gingin zui mai un.

[V7]
 Amah ging leh zuite ding ahi.</lyrics>
</song>